Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算今天和他分手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是谈了不久就告吹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害了他最重视之人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有他突然逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也没见面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我醒来发现他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样 恋爱总在萌芽时就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为他做的一切 也总是事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤 你真是没缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有真正被爱过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再喜欢人家 那样是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在交往的男朋友 悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我对他说喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是没什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想结束这单相思的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想把今天的约会作为美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…再也不想有那样的回忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打扮得挺漂亮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会吗 可别迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝盖没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚在家门口跌倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大的事我什么都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直在偷窥你哦 约会前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你穿的衣服很适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大不是也打扮了吗 很帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 花了点心思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的不是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号真差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没湿 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个送给他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 还是不想就这样结束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 这样很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着前面走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不知道他的邮箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您带来的那位…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是我带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心爱的包淋湿了 手机又丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大送我这种怪东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 知道今天是什么日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 请问是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是刚刚接到联系的山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡到你的手机了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 顺便给你送来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不请自来会不会给你造成麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也不知道工作什么时候能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面碰头比较困难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻烦您特地送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口有点渴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请我喝点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你男朋友有打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有留言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 好像搞错把小型驴装进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫小型驴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:13:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 给我打…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个无可救药的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优柔寡断 胆小怕事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又傻傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你更让人觉得可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 好像还什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒 停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 没中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 再见一次面确认下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让悠大吓一大跳 所以要乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个铃声是悠大打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机掉了 所以没法跟你联系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那个盒子里装着一个叫小型驴的动物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 装着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有胡闹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天不是也和男人在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你俩不是在耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有被真正爱过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…我今天可以早退吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得这么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么把那收拾干净你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小型驴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么吗 你住在前男友那了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是了 提不上前男友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像有个女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不能很好表达自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法表达爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想我这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱美希哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…昨天的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成悠大也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有恐高症啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去东京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司机师傅 请开快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很危险 你小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 你别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我那么任性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驴 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给悠大的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我找回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太危险 快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是 想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是在打工还是在家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是不由自主地会想你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你想象的那种人

Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:20.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの時の２人輝いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この恋は永遠と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕の隣りには君がもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君のとなりには僕はもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:32.46,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今まで見たことない泣き顔を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:36.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕は君の手を握ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:42.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を離せばもう逢えないよ 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔で別れたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:46.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}から言う マタアイマショウ マタアイマショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の前では強く優しく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頼られたかったよまさしく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けず嫌い 強がる芝居
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最後の最後も素直になれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの言葉に涙し 涙し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:01.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを言葉で励まし 励まし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:03.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}言葉の魔法はもうすぐ 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いい思い出となって消え去る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.52,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そして傷つけたことは謝らない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:11.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「でもありがとう」これ以上は言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目的地なんてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:15.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たどり着いたのあなたの優しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:17.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はそんなに強くない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:20.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悲しみ我慢してるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣いてもいいよ 僕も泣くから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:25.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日だけは許してよ神様
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.28,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:32.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今まで見たことない泣き顔を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:36.49,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕は君の手を握ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:42.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を離せばもう逢えないよ 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔で別れたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}から言う マタアイマショウ マタアイマショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:51.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いろんな人に愛されて 常にあなたはまぶしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.26,0:23:54.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だから嫉妬し ケンカし 涙し
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:56.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}これからはもう それも出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}お互い違う人好きになって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:01.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}お互い違う人生歩んで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「僕はとっても幸せでした」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:06.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私もとっても幸せでした」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:08.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか心からいなくなるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:11.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だからしたいよ 素晴らしい過去に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:13.57,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この恋を未来に誇れます
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:15.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙まみれ 笑顔でめくる明日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:18.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしてまずこの場で別れ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:20.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わかってる きっと逢うことないって
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:05.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気持ちはわりきれないよ 簡単に
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.36,0:25:11.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}反対にその思いを大切にすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.16,0:25:14.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}整理が出来るまで思えばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.71,0:25:17.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}会えなくて そばにいなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.75,0:25:20.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思うだけ 忘れないことだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.17,0:25:22.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.28,0:25:26.63,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと過ごした大切な日々
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.66,0:25:31.37,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この僕を優しく包んでくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:37.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}でも明日からはもう逢えないよ 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.10,0:25:40.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生まれ変わっても必ずマタアイマショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.20,0:25:46.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今まで見たことない泣き顔を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.60,0:25:50.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕は君の手を握ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.55,0:25:56.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を離せばもう逢えないよ 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.37,0:25:57.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔で別れたい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.85,0:26:01.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}から言う マタアイマショウ マタアイマショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.73,0:26:06.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と僕と
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.53,0:26:12.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悲しい別れがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.76,0:26:15.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}楽しいとき笑えるよな
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.24,0:26:17.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}逃げ出さず現実を受け止めた
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.82,0:26:20.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もちろん君に出会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:20.01,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾经以为我们两人之间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.47,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永恒不变的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.86,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如今我的身旁已不再有你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.01,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}而你的身旁我已…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:32.46,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看着从未见过的哭泣脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:36.31,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我握着你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:42.17,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦放开手 就再也见不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.76,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望带着笑容与你分手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:46.94,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我说「择日再相逢」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.41,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望在你面前既坚强又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.73,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能让你依赖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.14,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我装出好胜又逞强的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.35,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}到最后的最后都无法坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.82,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为你的话语而流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:01.30,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用话语给你鼓励
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:03.33,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼看言语的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.69,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}马上就要变成美好回忆 消失而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.52,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}对于伤害你的事不说道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:11.00,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但要对你说声谢谢 仅止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.76,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}原本就没有目标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:15.27,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我最后找到的是你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:17.73,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你并没有那么坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:20.30,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是不是强忍住悲伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.64,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}哭出来吧 我也会一起哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:25.17,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望上天原谅我们今天的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.28,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:32.56,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看着从未见过的哭泣脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:36.49,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我握着你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:42.18,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦放开手 就再也见不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.64,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望带着笑容与你分手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.90,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我说「择日再相逢」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:51.25,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被许多人爱着的你 总是那么耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.26,0:23:54.24,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我嫉妒 吵架 流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:56.44,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可是从今以后 这也成了奢望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.81,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此爱上不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:01.32,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}踏上不同的人生道路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.22,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我很幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:06.08,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我也很幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:08.53,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也许哪天会从彼此的心中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:11.11,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我宁愿把它当成一段美好的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:13.57,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与你的相恋是我未来的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:15.84,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我愿泪流满面的走向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:18.08,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}于是我们此时在这里分别
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:20.70,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中也知道一定不会再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:05.24,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}感情并非那么容易就能割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.36,0:25:11.15,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}反而不如将它留作珍贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.16,0:25:14.69,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在整理好心情之前 想起你也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.71,0:25:17.74,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不能见面 不在身边也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.75,0:25:20.17,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要想着就好 更不会遗忘…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.17,0:25:22.27,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.28,0:25:26.63,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾经与你一起度过那段珍贵的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.66,0:25:31.37,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}给了一个将我温柔包容的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:37.09,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不过明天开始就不能与你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.10,0:25:40.95,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望我们来生还能再相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.20,0:25:46.60,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看着从未见过的哭泣脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.60,0:25:50.54,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我握着你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.55,0:25:56.35,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦放开手 就再也见不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.37,0:25:57.81,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望带着笑容与你分手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.85,0:26:01.19,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我说「择日再相逢」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.73,0:26:06.04,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.53,0:26:12.70,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为有悲伤的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.76,0:26:15.22,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今后才有欢乐的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.24,0:26:17.82,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我毫不犹豫的接受了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.82,0:26:20.51,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}过与你的相遇依旧是我一生的幸福


